            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh no, what do I do...? I think I entered their territory..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x123,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sorry, I'll just be leaving now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x0,
            "voice_id": 0x233,
            "name_id": 0x55,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Cue cue cue cue!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x123,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hyaaah, I don't think he's gonna let me go. I need to protect myself!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Enemies wander freely around the Field Map. Press <IM04> to strike them with<CR>your staff and take the initiative."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "During battle, one gets KO'd if their HP falls to 0. You will be defeated if all allies' HP falls to 0."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Check the battle turn order on the Action Gauge on the right of the screen. Choose an action when it's your turn."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Depending on your distance and position in relation to your enemies, some actions may generate bonuses."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You earn EXP and money by winning battles, and sometimes items. You'll level up after a certain amount of EXP."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Also, enemies near towns aren't that strong, but as you reach more remote regions, stronger enemies will appear."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Those enemies are formidable and won't be easy to defeat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "To avoid wasting time and having your whole party get KO'd, prepare attack and heal items when you travel far."
        }
    ]
